Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:06.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}One morning on a day off from school, we went to the outskirts of Beika to do an art project for homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Could that be—?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the one that Adamski saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeking comprehensive answers,\Nhe solves every mystery and code!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A crashed UFO spotted at a riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:41.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was the victim hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, we know that—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't bring kids into a crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but they told me they were your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, even so you can't just—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an unlucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A UFO from the far reaches of space landed right on top of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! You can't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the aliens from the UFO yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? No, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that called a hit-and-run on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flap on this man's pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks like it caught on something and got torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But give me a break, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wearing really flashy clothing. What kind of person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was 22-years old Osamu Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from Beika Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is around 1 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was crushed by the UFO twice and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's all we know right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you know, you can leave—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said he was crushed twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were two wounds in different places on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there were no signs of life in the wound from the second impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it seems that he died when he was crushed the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to get in trouble if Inspector Megure sees you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My flying saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Please get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Taking it back? Who are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Me? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:46.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shōzō Onuma (58)\NUFO researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm a physics researcher, Shōzō Onuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,For 30 years, I've dedicated myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to developing this flying saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it didn't come from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:05:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's from my laboratory nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder how it flew here, it's still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To cover my research expenses,\NI work night shifts at a corner shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was working last night, and when I came back to the lab this morning, this was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when even the man who made it calls it incomplete,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then there's no way it could fly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Dr. Onuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that truck also at your laboratory last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I always leave it with the key inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I don't like having to look for the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what happened is pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The UFO didn't fly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody just brought it here with that truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's pretty simple when you put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got excited over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it didn't fly here, then how did he end up underneath the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Someone was pinned down by my saucer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We, the police, believe it was a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A homicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We think the killer knocked out Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and laid him down by the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he took your saucer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and dropped it from above the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the killer go through all that trouble to kill him with the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, Dr. Onuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you take me to your laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but could you return this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but it's a vital piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, kids. Leave the rest to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We have to go and do some sketches for homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you really make a flying saucer in a tiny place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came here to draw some sketches of this lab, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably looks dilapidated to keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, it won't attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! So there's gotta be supercomputers and lots of cool stuff inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go take a look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow I don't think it'll live up to their expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,Let the UFO fly to outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what do you think of Onuma Flying Saucer Research Laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's look for clues to find the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you keep the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was hanging over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dream about it flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So it was hanging from the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This looks very rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have fallen off when the killer took down the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it was weak to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there's a name on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hat must belong to the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the killer's name is Man'nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It belongs to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That scrap of fabric wasn't there yesterday either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, both Man'nen and the murdered Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From my research, Osamu Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a friend who was like a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the victim, Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:25.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the other guy is Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend, Sadao Man'nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:25.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sadao Man'nen (33)\NDebt Collector
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, they were at a restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:33.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll pay for all the bills tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, Buchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We have an idea that'll make us rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's plausible that they snuck into this place last night to try to get money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Man'nen were the criminal, why would he kill his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you really think they'd come {\i1}here{\i0} for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No offence, but nothing here looks like it's actually worth much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is! That treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Let the UFO fly to outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:11.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Let the UFO fly to outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought it at the end of last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was supposedly the work of a famous calligrapher, and I paid ¥50,000 for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,¥50,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seller, Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, said it was perfect for me, so he gave me a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōkura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinji Ōkura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinji Ōkura, the loan shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen and Iwabuchi were hired by him as debt collectors
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were Ōkura's underlings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believed he was guilty of tax evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He supposedly had about a hundred million in his assets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sometime during the beginning of the month, the revenue office investigated his house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but they couldn't find where he hid his wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, no hidden assets were ever found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was that type of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a money-worshipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He exaggerated that anything under a million yen was worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that he'd sell a fake scroll just to get ¥50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe the two men snuck in here under Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Kinji Ōkura died two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was involved in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he must be related to the case somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two men working under Ōkura snuck into the place of the man he sold the scroll to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't sound like a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen and Iwabuchi were with Kinji Ōkura at Beika Central Hospital when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is about Kinji Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who arrived here in an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were wondering how he seemed when he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he arrived, he was already unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right before his last breath, he said something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-You... foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were his last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'You foe'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, there's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be about that scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably regretted selling that fake thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's that admirable?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} loved money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the kind of dying message he'd leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is pretty obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinji Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} secretly had several hundred millions worth in assets...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his money wasn't found in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They even did a thorough investigation of his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was at the beginning of this month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right before that, Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sold the scroll to Dr. Onuma at the end of last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a person who considers anything below a million yen worthless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sell a scroll only to get fifty thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may have had a different reason for selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, there aren't many places as safe as that laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There would never be any robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! Ōkura sold the scroll to hide his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went to sell the scroll, and while the doctor wasn't looking, he hid the money somewhere in that laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With no chance of it being stolen, it'd be a safe temporary hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scroll was just an excuse to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't care about the fifty thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said right before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}U-UFO...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,UFO meant the saucer research lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen and Iwabuchi found out about the treasure's hiding spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wanted to take it for themselves, so they snuck into the place and found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while they were close friends, he didn't want to share the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so Sadao Man'nen killed Osamu Iwabuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was that, Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was from Beika Police Station, who we're having search for Sadao Man'nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to owe money to others in the same business,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he's still running away from the debt collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he has millions, wouldn't he just repay his debts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the money still hasn't been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our guess that Man'nen killed Iwabuchi to take the money for himself no longer holds true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So Sadao Man'nen doesn't have a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then who killed Osamu Iwabuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man'nen{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pretty strange, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he decided to stop looking for the money before he found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, when he brought the saucer out at 1 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened that made him stop searching?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the word... 'an unexpected situation'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unexpected situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something to do with the broken wire that the saucer was hanging from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wire it was hanging from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was one wire that was rusty and had broken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was crushed twice by the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died the first time and was crushed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unexpected situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A torn wire...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crushed twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Sadao Man'nen has no motive to kill Osamu Iwabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why isn't this a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I know is that the money's still hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, let's go back to the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you guys can go now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We left our stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many suitcases does a hundred million yen fill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be bars of gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you searching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was it hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} {\i0}never came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was never here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't he come to sell the scroll...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He contacted me, so I went to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:59.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I heard that you were building a flying saucer, so I knew it would be bad karma not to sell this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's as if it was written for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ain't that right? It can be a heirloom of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll give it to you for ¥50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's how I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinji Ōkura never came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he couldn't have hidden anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ōkura said 'UFO', I guess he wasn't talking about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two misunderstood him and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:34.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then why did Kinji Ōkura sell the scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:38.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He called Dr. Onuma just to sell that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, Man'nen will be coming here tonight to look for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wonder if he can wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to return it fast, or I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here. Lucky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Sadao Man'nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were here last night as well, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With your friend, Osamu Iwabuchi,\Nlooking for Kinji Ōkura's hidden fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you were caught in an unexpected situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It has to be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:38.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}'UFO' must mean this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, my only good suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can buy as many suits as you want when we get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Buchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A-Are you okay, Buchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Buchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was instantly squashed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to change it once I got money from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't continue searching for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you couldn't just leave the body there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the body was discovered the next morning, the police would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Iwabuchi was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would think that his best friend was also with him, and you would be suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, if during the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police found the money, you would have lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to prevent that, you came up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By moving both the body and the saucer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you tried to make it look like Iwabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died at the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To turn the officers' attention away from this lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was involved in a UFO landing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted people to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there would've been an easier method to distract the officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have hidden the body where people wouldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police wouldn't have investigated if the body wasn't discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have a funeral if his body wasn't found.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be fair to Buchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you understand what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've committed one crime after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trespassing in this laboratory.\NAbandoning Osamu Iwabuchi's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking the UFO out counts as theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I admit everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, about Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hidden wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jewels were hidden inside the scroll's metal bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōkura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dying words weren't indicating a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the UFO scroll itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll drive you guys home. Get your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We forgot to do our homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buried treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:02.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A Mystery Train Pass Ring?!
